channel.title: Connection time out when trying to connect to world
channel.description:
Ok so let me start off by saying that the dam port 43594 wont open. It says its in use but it never is (yes ive looked). Is there a way to just change the port my server uses to one that i can actually open? Im using the source Eclipse 639. Ty for any help :)
EDIT: Ok well now when i use http://canyouseeme.org/ it says it can see me (service). But it still says connection timed out when i try to connect to the world.
